1
00:01:06,500 --> 00:01:14,680
INVISIBLE WAVES

2
00:01:33,220 --> 00:01:34,930
That's for Noi?

3
00:01:36,970 --> 00:01:38,240
Oh, yes.

4
00:01:38,420 --> 00:01:39,960
You know her too.

5
00:01:41,540 --> 00:01:44,360
You're going to ask her to marry you?

6
00:01:46,010 --> 00:01:47,280
Tonight.

7
00:02:33,060 --> 00:02:34,770
Compliments of the boss.

8
00:02:45,740 --> 00:02:48,450
I still think this place is creepy.

9
00:02:48,970 --> 00:02:53,090
I hate seeing those machines.

10
00:02:54,060 --> 00:02:56,160
Something smells great!

11
00:02:57,020 --> 00:02:58,650
Dinner's almost ready.

12
00:02:58,900 --> 00:03:01,480
I meant you.

13
00:03:13,380 --> 00:03:15,210
Let's skip dinner...

14
00:03:15,380 --> 00:03:17,670
... and have dessert now.

15
00:03:18,090 --> 00:03:20,600
Oh, but I think you'll enjoy dinner more.

16
00:03:20,810 --> 00:03:22,970
You've been working too long
for my husband.

17
00:03:24,730 --> 00:03:28,080
You're starting to talk like him.

18
00:03:34,570 --> 00:03:36,640
I have to stir the sauce.

19
00:03:38,220 --> 00:03:40,210
I love it when you talk like that!

20
00:03:42,250 --> 00:03:44,760
Seiko, the sauce will be ruined
if I don't stir it.

21
00:03:45,450 --> 00:03:47,960
That's okay.
I like my sauce medium-ruined.

22
00:04:19,370 --> 00:04:21,720
Well, that was delicious, darling...

23
00:04:22,370 --> 00:04:24,090
... as always.

24
00:04:24,290 --> 00:04:25,920
Did you have enough?

25
00:04:27,050 --> 00:04:29,440
I might have room for something more.

26
00:04:29,620 --> 00:04:31,090
I made chocolate mousse.

27
00:04:31,460 --> 00:04:35,160
Oh well, there's room for that too.

28
00:04:45,260 --> 00:04:46,610
I'll get some more wine.

29
00:04:46,780 --> 00:04:50,080
Okay, darling. You're the boss.

30
00:04:50,580 --> 00:04:53,290
Oh, wait a minute.
Actually, you're not the boss.

31
00:04:59,020 --> 00:05:00,530
Oops, sorry darling.

32
00:05:02,020 --> 00:05:04,360
Come on, get the mousse and hurry back.

33
00:05:09,020 --> 00:05:11,210
Oh, I like this.

34
00:05:12,180 --> 00:05:15,040
Let's turn it up a bit, okay?

35
00:05:15,570 --> 00:05:18,490
The neighbors won't mind, will they?

36
00:05:20,180 --> 00:05:23,520
I have only one neighbor.
She won't mind.

37
00:05:28,930 --> 00:05:32,040
You don't look like
your father at all, you know?

38
00:05:40,410 --> 00:05:42,920
You still don't have a TV?

39
00:05:43,420 --> 00:05:44,890
What do you do when you're alone?

40
00:05:45,140 --> 00:05:46,080
I sleep.

41
00:05:46,580 --> 00:05:49,090
But how do you know
what's going on in the world?

42
00:05:49,260 --> 00:05:50,560
I already know.

43
00:05:50,820 --> 00:05:53,010
There's always war.

44
00:05:56,530 --> 00:05:58,130
You are so cynical, darling.

45
00:06:02,180 --> 00:06:03,490
Kiss me.

46
00:06:06,620 --> 00:06:07,890
Are you drunk?

47
00:06:09,620 --> 00:06:12,170
Why? You gonna take advantage
of me if I'm drunk?

48
00:06:19,250 --> 00:06:21,710
You still have to eat your mousse.

49
00:09:53,890 --> 00:09:55,080
Good morning.

50
00:11:28,890 --> 00:11:30,400
W RESTAURANT

51
00:11:43,660 --> 00:11:45,320
The restaurant's closed.

52
00:11:45,580 --> 00:11:46,770
Go home.

53
00:11:47,530 --> 00:11:49,080
Good morning, boss.

54
00:11:52,170 --> 00:11:53,640
You want some cigarette?

55
00:11:54,170 --> 00:11:56,890
No, thanks. I don't feel so good.

56
00:11:58,770 --> 00:12:00,250
Go home and pack.

57
00:12:03,250 --> 00:12:04,480
Kyoji!

58
00:12:09,740 --> 00:12:11,490
You have a good vacation.

59
00:12:37,610 --> 00:12:38,520
Hello.

60
00:12:38,900 --> 00:12:40,090
Hello.

61
00:12:40,260 --> 00:12:41,450
I am Kyoji.

62
00:12:41,650 --> 00:12:43,010
Do you know me?

63
00:12:44,010 --> 00:12:46,930
No, I don't know you.

64
00:12:48,420 --> 00:12:50,610
But I know why you're here.

65
00:12:51,340 --> 00:12:53,440
You are a little bit early.

66
00:12:53,620 --> 00:12:56,440
Come worship first.

67
00:12:56,700 --> 00:12:58,570
I'll be with you later.

68
00:13:14,770 --> 00:13:16,080
Did you pray?

69
00:13:17,090 --> 00:13:18,010
No.

70
00:13:18,290 --> 00:13:19,320
Why not?

71
00:13:20,330 --> 00:13:22,400
I didn't come here for that.

72
00:13:22,610 --> 00:13:24,090
I see.

73
00:13:24,290 --> 00:13:25,600
You came here for this, I believe.

74
00:13:26,890 --> 00:13:28,280
I think so.

75
00:13:28,930 --> 00:13:31,090
Everything you want is inside there.

76
00:13:31,340 --> 00:13:34,050
The ticket, the money, the documents.

77
00:13:35,660 --> 00:13:37,920
I'll send you more money...

78
00:13:38,130 --> 00:13:39,440
... when you're in Phuket.

79
00:13:42,250 --> 00:13:44,320
This is very important

80
00:13:46,780 --> 00:13:48,930
Your life now depends on it.

81
00:13:50,140 --> 00:13:52,200
Lizard's contact number is inside.

82
00:13:52,410 --> 00:13:53,680
Lizard?

83
00:13:54,020 --> 00:13:55,490
Yes, from now on...

84
00:13:56,650 --> 00:13:58,440
... he's the one you'll have to contact.

85
00:13:59,540 --> 00:14:01,010
Any problem...

86
00:14:01,530 --> 00:14:02,920
... contact Lizard.

87
00:14:03,370 --> 00:14:05,840
Remember, Lizard.

88
00:14:06,140 --> 00:14:08,130
Only Lizard.

89
00:14:08,330 --> 00:14:09,720
He's your man.

90
00:14:10,130 --> 00:14:12,290
Your only contact with the past.

91
00:14:17,540 --> 00:14:19,560
Can you give this to the boss?

92
00:14:24,220 --> 00:14:27,210
Okay, I'll take care of it.

93
00:14:27,580 --> 00:14:29,000
Have a good life.

94
00:14:30,740 --> 00:14:32,610
Are you really a monk?

95
00:14:35,060 --> 00:14:36,410
My father was.

96
00:15:42,460 --> 00:15:43,490
Hi, Maria.

97
00:15:43,740 --> 00:15:45,330
Oh, you're back.

98
00:15:45,580 --> 00:15:47,530
What did you do
to your apartment last night?

99
00:15:47,730 --> 00:15:49,520
It smells horrible!

100
00:15:50,410 --> 00:15:51,770
Leave the door open.

101
00:15:52,020 --> 00:15:54,040
Can I wash up at your place?

102
00:15:54,250 --> 00:15:55,610
Sure, go ahead.

103
00:15:55,810 --> 00:15:57,600
I'll make dinner tonight.

104
00:16:09,130 --> 00:16:12,640
So, you're leaving tomorrow, huh?

105
00:16:12,980 --> 00:16:14,760
That's a big surprise.

106
00:16:16,340 --> 00:16:18,090
Are you all ready.

107
00:16:19,130 --> 00:16:20,480
I guess.

108
00:16:21,420 --> 00:16:23,410
My boy's always ready.

109
00:16:25,260 --> 00:16:27,250
What do you think about leaving?

110
00:16:28,370 --> 00:16:30,210
I'm going to miss you.

111
00:16:31,060 --> 00:16:32,280
I know.

112
00:16:34,020 --> 00:16:35,280
I'll write to you.

113
00:16:35,540 --> 00:16:36,920
From the ship?

114
00:16:39,660 --> 00:16:41,200
I'll write to you.

115
00:16:42,970 --> 00:16:45,210
Okay. I'll wait for that.

116
00:16:50,010 --> 00:16:51,920
Hello? Are you Lizard?

117
00:16:52,130 --> 00:16:53,680
I'm leaving now.

118
00:16:54,940 --> 00:16:56,070
Bon Voyage.

119
00:16:58,370 --> 00:17:00,240
When I get to Phuket I'll call you.

120
00:17:00,500 --> 00:17:02,160
Have a good life.

121
00:17:41,820 --> 00:17:43,450
Can I help you, sir?

122
00:17:51,930 --> 00:17:54,840
I think you got the wrong room, sir.

123
00:17:55,180 --> 00:17:57,410
I can show you your room.

124
00:17:57,610 --> 00:17:59,120
Follow me, please.

125
00:19:50,500 --> 00:19:52,210
Wha...? What the...?

126
00:19:52,490 --> 00:19:53,440
What in the...?

127
00:19:57,930 --> 00:20:00,760
May we have your attention please.

128
00:20:01,170 --> 00:20:05,090
Universal Cruise will depart
Hong Kong shortly.

129
00:20:17,770 --> 00:20:20,720
May we have your attention please.

130
00:20:21,060 --> 00:20:24,880
Universal Cruise will depart
Hong Kong shortly.

131
00:21:07,610 --> 00:21:12,000
Lunch will be served shortly
at all of our restaurants...

132
00:21:12,260 --> 00:21:18,010
... Galaxy Cuisine, Tropical Cuisine,
